snippet.title: Pinball Deluxe (GB)
snippet.description:
Playthrough of Pinball Deluxe (GB), beating the highscores on all seven tables.


This took me more than five hours, around four of which were spent on the second table, which has a terrible habit of randomly dropping my ball.
